channel.description:
Randomly generates a students profile:

ex. 

[php]
First Name : Daniel 
Last Name : Saw
Gender : Male
Weigth   : 190 Lbs.
Heigth : 5 feet 2 inches
Room   : 7
[/php]

[php]
First Name : Stephany 
Last Name : Gredath
Gender : Female
Weigth   : 190 Lbs.
Heigth : 5 feet 5 inches
Room   : 8
[/php]

or my favorite:

[php]
First Name : Harmony
Last Name : Chua
Gender : Female
Weigth   : 130 Lbs.
Heigth : 5 feet 4 inches
Room   : 8
[/php]





